{% comment %}
  Article Text Section
  Numbered section with title and body text with drop cap
{% endcomment %}

<section
  class="article-section"
  style="
    --as-bg: {{ section.settings.background_color }};
    --as-number-color: {{ section.settings.number_color }};
    --as-title-color: {{ section.settings.title_color }};
    --as-title-size: {{ section.settings.title_size }}px;
    --as-title-size-mobile: {{ section.settings.title_size_mobile }}px;
    --as-text-color: {{ section.settings.text_color }};
    --as-text-size: {{ section.settings.text_size }}px;
    --as-text-size-mobile: {{ section.settings.text_size_mobile }}px;
    --as-dropcap-color: {{ section.settings.dropcap_color }};
    --as-dropcap-size: {{ section.settings.dropcap_size }}px;
    --as-dropcap-size-mobile: {{ section.settings.dropcap_size_mobile }}px;
    --as-divider-color: {{ section.settings.divider_color }};
    --as-padding-top: {{ section.settings.padding_top }}px;
    --as-padding-bottom: {{ section.settings.padding_bottom }}px;
    --as-padding-top-mobile: {{ section.settings.padding_top_mobile }}px;
    --as-padding-bottom-mobile: {{ section.settings.padding_bottom_mobile }}px;
  "
>
  <div class="article-section__container">
    <div class="article-section__grid">
      <div class="article-section__header">
        <div class="article-section__divider"></div>
        {%- if section.settings.section_number != blank or section.settings.section_label != blank -%}
          <p class="article-section__number">
            {%- if section.settings.section_number != blank -%}
              {{ section.settings.section_number }}.
            {%- endif -%}
            {%- if section.settings.section_label != blank -%}
              {{ section.settings.section_label | upcase }}
            {%- endif -%}
          </p>
        {%- endif -%}
        {%- if section.settings.title != blank -%}
          <h2 class="article-section__title">{{ section.settings.title }}</h2>
        {%- endif -%}
      </div>

      <div class="article-section__content">
        {%- if section.settings.body_text != blank -%}
          <div class="article-section__text {% if section.settings.enable_dropcap %}article-section__text--dropcap{% endif %}">
            {{ section.settings.body_text }}
          </div>
        {%- endif -%}
        {%- if section.settings.body_text_2 != blank -%}
          <div class="article-section__text article-section__text--secondary">
            {{ section.settings.body_text_2 }}
          </div>
        {%- endif -%}
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

{% stylesheet %}
  .article-section {
    background-color: var(--as-bg);
    padding: var(--as-padding-top-mobile) var(--page-margin) var(--as-padding-bottom-mobile);
  }

  .article-section__container {
    max-width: var(--page-width);
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .article-section__grid {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }

  .article-section__header {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: flex-start;
  }

  .article-section__divider {
    width: 60px;
    height: 1px;
    background-color: var(--as-divider-color);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .article-section__number {
    font-family: var(--font-body-family), sans-serif;
    font-size: 10px;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--as-number-color);
    margin: 0 0 0.75rem;
  }

  .article-section__title {
    font-family: var(--font-heading-family), serif;
    font-size: var(--as-title-size-mobile);
    font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--as-title-color);
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.2;
  }

  .article-section__content {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }

  .article-section__text {
    font-family: var(--font-heading-family), serif;
    font-size: var(--as-text-size-mobile);
    font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--as-text-color);
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .article-section__text p {
    margin: 0 0 1.25em;
  }

  .article-section__text p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  /* Drop cap styling */
  .article-section__text--dropcap p:first-of-type::first-letter,
  .article-section__text--dropcap > *:first-child::first-letter {
    font-family: var(--font-heading-family), serif;
    font-size: var(--as-dropcap-size-mobile);
    font-weight: 400;
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--as-dropcap-color);
    float: left;
    line-height: 0.8;
    margin-right: 0.15em;
    margin-top: 0.1em;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .article-section {
      padding: var(--as-padding-top) var(--page-margin) var(--as-padding-bottom);
    }

    .article-section__grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.5fr;
      gap: 4rem;
      align-items: flex-start;
    }

    .article-section__number {
      font-size: 11px;
    }

    .article-section__title {
      font-size: var(--as-title-size);
    }

    .article-section__text {
      font-size: var(--as-text-size);
    }

    .article-section__text--dropcap p:first-of-type::first-letter,
    .article-section__text--dropcap > *:first-child::first-letter {
      font-size: var(--as-dropcap-size);
      margin-right: 0.2em;
    }

    .article-section__content {
      gap: 2rem;
      max-width: 600px;
    }
  }
{% endstylesheet %}

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "Article section",
  "settings": [
    {
      "type": "header",
      "content": "Header"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "section_number",
      "label": "Section number",
      "default": "01"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "section_label",
      "label": "Section label",
      "default": "THE PROBLEM"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "title",
      "label": "Title",
      "default": "The Tyranny of the Grid"
    },
    {
      "type": "header",
      "content": "Content"
    },
    {
      "type": "richtext",
      "id": "body_text",
      "label": "Body text (paragraph 1)",
      "default": "<p>There is a quiet tyranny in the modern ceiling grid. The recessed can light, ubiquitous in construction since the late 1990s, was invented for offices, factories, and hospitals—places of hyper-vigilance, not sanctuaries of rest. It provides what lighting designers call \"general illumination\"—a flat, shadowless wash that ensures you can see the floor, but feel absolutely nothing.</p>"
    },
    {
      "type": "richtext",
      "id": "body_text_2",
      "label": "Body text (paragraph 2)",
      "default": "<p>To reclaim the home, we must reclaim the shadow. We must stop trying to simulate the noon sun inside our living rooms at 8 PM. We must embrace the cave. This is where the philosophy of the \"Layered Home\" begins.</p>"
    },
    {
      "type": "checkbox",
      "id": "enable_dropcap",
